Config/Properties/Simple version 0.07
=====================================

This package provides a simple access to properties configuration
files mixin functionality in packages Config::Properties and
Config::Find.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Config::Properties
  Condig::Find

